Package fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.impl

Class TreeGraph<N extends TreeGraphNode,​E extends ALEdge>

java.lang.Object
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.graph.impl.TreeGraph<N,​E>
Type Parameters:
N - The implementation of Node used in this graph (TreeGraphNode or a sub-class)
E - The implementation of Edge used in this graph (ALEdge or a sub-class)
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.cnrs.iees.omhtk.Textable, EdgeSet<E>, NodeSet<N>, Tree<N>
public class TreeGraph<N extends TreeGraphNode,​E extends ALEdge> extends Object implements Tree<N>, EdgeSet<E>, fr.cnrs.iees.omhtk.Textable

Implementation of a "treegraph", i.e. a graph with an internal tree structure or a tree with cross-links between its nodes.

Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 15 mai 2019
